    <scopecontent>
      <head>Scope and Content Information</head>
      <p>With these are related items including a Hemings family
         genealogy tracing descendants of Betty Hemings; several
         versions of an article "The Black Family at Monticello";
         copies of other articles with pertinent information; and other
         Jefferson related writings by Langhorne including a grant
         proposal for a biography of Martha Jefferson Randolph.</p>
    </scopecontent>
